    "text": "This tutorial shows examples of how to use some of the most common CSS elements in a VTT room. A full CSS tutorial is beyond the scope of VTT. There are many available on the web, including a good one at https://www.w3schools.com/css/default.asp. For other examples of how to use CSS to customize the apperance of buttons (or really any widget), look at the Button Appearance tutorial."
